## 2. File Structure

### Single Component (simple)

```
components/ui/
  Button.tsx              # Component + variants
  Button.stories.tsx      # Storybook stories
  Button.test.tsx         # Unit tests
```

### Compound Component (complex)

```
components/ui/data-table/
  index.ts                # Public API (re-exports)
  DataTable.tsx           # Root component
  DataTableHeader.tsx     # Sub-component
  DataTableRow.tsx        # Sub-component
  DataTablePagination.tsx # Sub-component
  data-table.types.ts     # Shared types
  data-table.utils.ts     # Helper functions
  DataTable.stories.tsx   # Stories
  DataTable.test.tsx      # Tests
```

### Domain Component

```
components/{{COMPONENT_PREFIX}}/loads/
  LoadCard.tsx
  LoadStatusBadge.tsx
  LoadCard.stories.tsx
```

### Directory Organization

```
components/
  ui/                     # Shared primitives (Button, Input, Dialog, etc.)
  {{COMPONENT_PREFIX}}/   # Domain-specific components
    loads/                # Load management components
    carriers/             # Carrier components
    shared/               # Shared domain components (DotLabel, etc.)
  layout/                 # Layout components (Sidebar, Header, PageShell)
  providers/              # Context providers (ThemeProvider, AuthProvider)
```

